  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/f85714fac1e98df797d0852cb1750c06.avif?t=1767849896\" width=614 height=802 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join our Discord ! The best place to report a bug and join the community.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Next Patch features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fix bugs with UI menus</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Implement Ray Tracing to improve Graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various minor bugs that have been reported by players</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Future RoadMap Goals</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphical Improvements to the various environments and characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Performance Improvements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adding more missions bringing the total number of unique missions to over 40!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adding new enemy types such as flying drones that can attack the player from the air</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adding teammate AI that will allow players who play singleplayer to control a squad of AI controlled police.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more to come !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What has already been updated ?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Global</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Bridge Mission in Valermo</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Singleplayer can now heal with large health syringe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Added new flying drones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rework of all of the police commander voices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Helicopter now shoot rockets at the player, making them even more deadly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved the dog, civilians and enemies AI</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Technical</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Added HLOD models for large complex buildings. This should improve performance in certain areas of the maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rework footstep sounds and improved the footstep spatialization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Performance on moving trains, inside places</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more in the patch notes!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/dcbee4e1be813948ba3e2aa300d9ce15.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/dcbee4e1be813948ba3e2aa300d9ce15.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=187 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Gooseman, the inventor of the original Counter-Strike mod, comes Alpha Response, a fast paced singleplayer / co-op experience that puts you in the boots of elite police forces worldwide. Inspired by arcade action games from the 90s, such as, Virtua Cop, Time Crisis, the firefights in Alpha Response are very dynamic and will push the player to their limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Respond to critical situations requiring surgical precision to save innocent lives. Every decision matters in a world where threats lurk around every corner. Bring justice to criminals and terrorists that are bringing chaos to the streets using a wide arsenal of weapons and equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/c9ce9f497b1ac2ff524d9fa0f9c91ff4.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/c9ce9f497b1ac2ff524d9fa0f9c91ff4.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a global police initiative battling cross-border criminal syndicates. Choose your elite unit and take the fight to the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with 3 friends in explosive 4-player co-op or take on the challenge solo with AI controlled teammates. Coordination and fast reflexes are key - your survival depends on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/93f023f30a0ee25c75ea178a43ea0dba.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/93f023f30a0ee25c75ea178a43ea0dba.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/28b44f7f630feb53ea18a1eee5dece54.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/28b44f7f630feb53ea18a1eee5dece54.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alpha Response features heart-racing dynamic missions from hostage rescues to bomb threats with multiple approaches to tackle each mission. Enemies spawn differently each time and can enter the mission by vehicle or on foot and the player will need to be aware of his surroundings at all times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/e699209a41f9ff786b40a5baab32de6b.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/e699209a41f9ff786b40a5baab32de6b.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight across massive, detailed environments from city streets and massive metro stations to towering cathedrals and industrial complexes. Navigate indoor and outdoor battlegrounds teeming with civilians who need your protection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ffbcaeab3f68402d61ab18548cbe4088.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ffbcaeab3f68402d61ab18548cbe4088.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ffbcaeab3f68402d61ab18548cbe4088.mp4?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/b1486fa48c641bb954cef5d3ed0df46e.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/b1486fa48c641bb954cef5d3ed0df46e.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a lethal variety of opponents - hardened criminals, attack dogs, flying drones, armored vehicles, and helicopter gunships. Each threat demands unique tactics to overcome and you'll always be kept on your toes throughout the mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/7e904378fa43c37fe8c36de18c24bce8.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/7e904378fa43c37fe8c36de18c24bce8.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/7e904378fa43c37fe8c36de18c24bce8.mp4?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/a8fd3e1ce122a4f1600be3859b017c82.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/a8fd3e1ce122a4f1600be3859b017c82.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dominate with an extensive arsenal from sidearms to heavy weaponry. Deploy shields, grenades, and vehicles to gain the tactical edge. Every tool is essential for mission success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ae6f9f2bfdd9264ea52078559133547c.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ae6f9f2bfdd9264ea52078559133547c.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ae6f9f2bfdd9264ea52078559133547c.mp4?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/dcbee4e1be813948ba3e2aa300d9ce15.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/dcbee4e1be813948ba3e2aa300d9ce15.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=187 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Gooseman, the inventor of the original Counter-Strike mod, comes Alpha Response, a fast paced singleplayer / co-op experience that puts you in the boots of elite police forces worldwide. Inspired by arcade action games from the 90s, such as, Virtua Cop, Time Crisis, the firefights in Alpha Response are very dynamic and will push the player to their limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Respond to critical situations requiring surgical precision to save innocent lives. Every decision matters in a world where threats lurk around every corner. Bring justice to criminals and terrorists that are bringing chaos to the streets using a wide arsenal of weapons and equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/c9ce9f497b1ac2ff524d9fa0f9c91ff4.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/c9ce9f497b1ac2ff524d9fa0f9c91ff4.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a global police initiative battling cross-border criminal syndicates. Choose your elite unit and take the fight to the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with 3 friends in explosive 4-player co-op or take on the challenge solo with AI controlled teammates. Coordination and fast reflexes are key - your survival depends on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/93f023f30a0ee25c75ea178a43ea0dba.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/93f023f30a0ee25c75ea178a43ea0dba.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/28b44f7f630feb53ea18a1eee5dece54.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/28b44f7f630feb53ea18a1eee5dece54.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alpha Response features heart-racing dynamic missions from hostage rescues to bomb threats with multiple approaches to tackle each mission. Enemies spawn differently each time and can enter the mission by vehicle or on foot and the player will need to be aware of his surroundings at all times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/e699209a41f9ff786b40a5baab32de6b.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/e699209a41f9ff786b40a5baab32de6b.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight across massive, detailed environments from city streets and massive metro stations to towering cathedrals and industrial complexes. Navigate indoor and outdoor battlegrounds teeming with civilians who need your protection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ffbcaeab3f68402d61ab18548cbe4088.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ffbcaeab3f68402d61ab18548cbe4088.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ffbcaeab3f68402d61ab18548cbe4088.mp4?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/b1486fa48c641bb954cef5d3ed0df46e.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/b1486fa48c641bb954cef5d3ed0df46e.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a lethal variety of opponents - hardened criminals, attack dogs, flying drones, armored vehicles, and helicopter gunships. Each threat demands unique tactics to overcome and you'll always be kept on your toes throughout the mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/7e904378fa43c37fe8c36de18c24bce8.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/7e904378fa43c37fe8c36de18c24bce8.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/7e904378fa43c37fe8c36de18c24bce8.mp4?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/a8fd3e1ce122a4f1600be3859b017c82.avif?t=1767849896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras_big/a8fd3e1ce122a4f1600be3859b017c82.avif?t=1767849896 width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dominate with an extensive arsenal from sidearms to heavy weaponry. Deploy shields, grenades, and vehicles to gain the tactical edge. Every tool is essential for mission success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ae6f9f2bfdd9264ea52078559133547c.poster.avif?t=1767849896\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ae6f9f2bfdd9264ea52078559133547c.webm?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089250/extras/ae6f9f2bfdd9264ea52078559133547c.mp4?t=1767849896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
